description:
It's funny to me that my fanboys are bending over backwards to give me everything I've ever wanted, when all I've ever wanted is this little microphone. See, this, this is power. This voice is power. In anybody else's hands, this is just a microphone, in my hands, it's a pipe bomb.

Tomoyasu Hotei - Battle Without Honor or Humanity

TMNT 4 (SNES) Music - Big Apple, 3 A.M.
Genesis - Dancing with the Moonlit Knight
Edgar Winter Group - Frankenstein (8 bit cover)
Smooth McGroove - Dire Dire Docks Acapella
Cave Story Theme
Lemon Demon - The Ultimate Showdown of Ultimate Destiny (Instrumental)
Jeff Lorber - Tune 88
Lemon Jelly - Homage to Patagonia 
Emerson Lake & Palmer - Tarkus
Gorillaz - Double Bass
GlitchxCity - Hoenn Elite 4 Remix
Led Zeppelin - Achilles Last Stand (Instrumental)
Pink Floyd - Shine on You Crazy Diamond (Part IX)
Centz - The London Underground
